column_description: Foreign key referencing the `Properties` table, indicating the property to which the room belongs
Unique identifier for the room within the property, typically a number or code
Foreign key referencing the `Ref_Room_Types` table, indicating the type of room (e.g., living room, kitchen, bedroom)
Size classification of the room, such as small (s), medium (m), or large (l)
Additional descriptive information about the room, if any
